      "rationale": "The multisite observational dataset covers the full COU flow-speed envelope. Clinical perfusion records confirm that all five target operating points (3 L/min/2500 RPM, 4 L/min/2800 RPM, 4 L/min/3200 RPM, 5 L/min/3000 RPM, 6 L/min/3500 RPM) are represented by at least 18 perfusion episodes each, providing adequate coverage of the intended use envelope."
