      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted RH values within ±15% of reference values at all five operating points; RH < 1.0 at all points.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted RH values compared against the observational dataset median at each of the five operating points. Maximum deviation was 11.7% at the 6 L/min/3500 RPM condition. All predicted RH values were below 1.0, satisfying the acceptance criterion. The observational study provides a large reference population (312 episodes) that the assessment team considers sufficient to establish a credible reference baseline, and the agreement is judged to confirm model predictive capability for identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions."
    },
